name: Tellwut Corp.
overview:
Tellwut® is an internet community of online survey takers that provide crowdsourcing and market intelligence opportunities to organizations.

Tellwut’s North American online community of individuals are dedicated to expressing their opinions through online surveys based upon a wide variety of topics in exchange for rewards and the Tellwut community experience. The Tellwut community and proprietary software application provide a platform for organizations to send surveys to their stakeholders or to conduct their own online market research through the use of the Tellwut survey platform and the Tellwut Community allowing businesses to gain a clearer understanding and insight into their products or services, customer attitudes and potential business opportunities.
